The one billionth download of a digital single in the UK took place last night.

According to the Official Charts Company, the UK reached the milestone thanks to artists such as Adele and Maroon 5.

The company's figures show that Adele's Someone Like You is the most downloaded track ever in the UK - it has been downloaded 1.46 million times.

